    public class HandlerPanel
extends SimplePanel
implements SourcesClickEvents, SourcesMouseEvents, SourcesMouseWheelEvents, HasAllDragAndDropHandlers, HasAllMouseHandlers, HasClickHandlers, HasDoubleClickHandlers, HasAllKeyHandlers, HasAllFocusHandlers, HasAllGestureHandlers, HasAllTouchHandlers
    A simple panel that adds the ability to catch mouse and keyboard events. Use instead of FocusPanel.
